PN,44501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FA police officer has said he cannot
OL,8,Fexplain why he stated in evidence at
OL,9,Fthe inquest into the death of Noah
OL,10,FDonohoe that he had been tasked to
OL,11,Fsearch for a green coat belonging to
OL,12,Fthe missing schoolboy.
OL,14,FThe constable initially told a jury at
OL,15,FBelfast Coroner's Court he had
OL,16,Fsearched a flat for the missing coat,
OL,17,Fbut later conceded he "didn't believe"
OL,18,Fhe had been told about the item.
OL,26,@yD@WOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FThe officer also told the inquest he
OL,8,Fhad been "briefed" by a team at
OL,9,FMusgrave Street police station in
OL,10,FBelfast before giving evidence on
OL,11,FThursday.
OL,13,FThe inquest into the death of the
OL,14,Fschoolboy, which is being heard with a
OL,15,Fjury, is in its ninth week.
OL,26,@pD@JOUpD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,8,Fwas 14 when his naked body was found
OL,9,Fin a storm drain tunnel in north
OL,10,FBelfast in June 2020, six days after
OL,11,Fhe left home on his bike to meet two
OL,12,Ffriends in the Cavehill area of the
OL,13,Fcity.
OL,15,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,16,Fcause of death was likely to be
OL,17,Fdrowning.
OL,19,FThe inquest continued on Thursday with
OL,20,Fevidence from Constable Wharry.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FHe told the jury that on June 25 2020,
OL,8,Ffour days after Noah disappeared, he
OL,9,Fwas tasked to assist CID with the
OL,10,Farrest of a male at a flat in Belfast.
OL,12,FThe officer said nobody was in
OL,13,Fattendance at the address, but it was
OL,14,Fsearched and shortly before 10pm he
OL,15,Fdiscovered items of schoolwork
OL,16,Fbelonging to Noah in a rubbish bag in
OL,17,Fthe kitchen of the flat.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FCounsel to the coroner Peter Coll
OL,8,Fasked if the person police had been
OL,9,Ftasked to arrest on the evening was
OL,10,FDaryl Paul.
OL,12,FThe officer confirmed this.
OL,14,FPaul, of Cliftonville Avenue,
OL,15,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to stealing
OL,16,Fa rucksack containing Noah's laptop
OL,17,Fand school books.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FThe officer told the court he had been
OL,8,Fadvised that Noah's laptop, bag and
OL,9,Fgreen coat were in the possession of
OL,10,FPaul.
OL,12,FThe officer said the flat was
OL,13,F"extensively" searched but the laptop
OL,14,Fand green coat were not present.
OL,16,FHe said the school books were bagged
OL,17,Fand taken to Musgrave Street police
OL,18,Fstation.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FThe officer told the court that
OL,8,Fdespite stating in his original
OL,9,Fstatement there was body-worn camera
OL,10,Fevidence of the search, he later said
OL,11,Fhe could not remember if footage had
OL,12,Fbeen recorded.
OL,14,FThe witness was then questioned by
OL,15,Fcounsel for Noah's mother Fiona
OL,16,FDonohoe.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FBrenda Campbell KC showed the witness
OL,8,Fa statement from Ms Donohoe setting
OL,9,Fout her concerns about the police
OL,10,Finvestigation into the disappearance
OL,11,Fof her son, including the failure to
OL,12,Frecover items of his clothing.
OL,14,FShe said: "Did you understand before
OL,15,Fyou got into the witness box today
OL,16,Fthat a concern was the failure of the
OL,17,Fpolice to look for Noah's green coat?"
OL,26,@vD@KOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FThe officer said he had been "briefed"
OL,8,Fat Musgrave Street police station
OL,9,Fbefore he gave evidence that there had
OL,10,Fbeen concerns about the coat.
OL,12,FMs Campbell said: "It is a concern
OL,13,Fthat for the first time in your
OL,14,Fevidence, you mentioned three or four
OL,15,Ftimes a green coat... and yet it
OL,16,Fappears nowhere in your statements,
OL,17,Fnowhere in your contemporaneous
OL,18,Fnotebook.
OL,26,@oD@^OUoD@fO]tD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,F"You tell us today for the first time
OL,8,Fyou were briefed in relation to the
OL,9,Fgreen coat, that you looked for the
OL,10,Fgreen coat and that you didn't find
OL,11,Fthe green coat."
OL,13,FHe said: "I looked for all the items
OL,14,Fwe were told to look for."
OL,16,FThe barrister said: "Which you tell us
OL,17,Ffor the first time included the green
OL,18,Fcoat. Is that true?"
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@PO]uD@JOUvD@ZO]xD@UOUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FHe said: "I believe so. We were in the
OL,8,Fflat, when Daryl Paul was not there we
OL,9,Fwere told items."
OL,11,FMs Campbell said: "What were you told?"
OL,13,FThe officer responded: "The laptop and
OL,14,Fthe bag."
OL,16,FShe continued: "Anything else?"
OL,18,FMr Wharry said: "I don't believe we
OL,19,Fwere told about the green coat.
OL,21,F"We were told about items."
OL,26,@oD@JOUqD@QO]sD@SOUsD@gO]uD@XOUvD@IO]xD@
OL,26,APOUxD@_O]zD@QOU}D@AOU}D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FMs Campbell said: "You don't believe
OL,8,Fyou were told about the green coat,
OL,9,Fwhy have you told us repeatedly this
OL,10,Fmorning that you were?"
OL,12,FWhen the officer did not reply, the
OL,13,Fbarrister asked if he was able to
OL,14,Fanswer the question.
OL,16,FHe said: "I am not, no."
OL,18,FMs Campbell said this was a "serious
OL,19,Fmatter" and "difficult evidence" for
OL,20,FNoah's mother to listen to.
OL,26,@oD@SOUrD@WO]xD@JOUxD@XO]zD@]OU{D@GO]{D@
OL,26,AMOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FAfter lunch, Ms Campbell asked: "You
OL,8,Ftold us you had been briefed by the
OL,9,Fteam at Musgrave Street station before
OL,10,Fyou came to court today. Who was
OL,11,Fpresent?"
OL,13,FCoroner Mr Justice Rooney warned the
OL,14,Fwitness that he was not obliged to
OL,15,Frespond if he felt a truthful answer
OL,16,Fwould incriminate himself.
OL,26,@oD@aOUsD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FThe witness indicated he would answer
OL,8,Fthe question and said he was briefed
OL,9,Fby two other officers about the "the
OL,10,Frunning order of the court" as he had
OL,11,Fnever been in the witness box before.
OL,13,FMs Campbell pointed out the officer
OL,14,Fhad said in his first statement to the
OL,15,Finquest that, on the evening he had
OL,16,Fcarried out the search of the flat,
OL,17,Fthe events had been captured on body-
OL,18,Fworn video footage.
OL,20,FShe said: "Was that the truth?"
OL,26,@qD@aOUrD@[O]|D@KOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FThe officer said: "I believed it was
OL,8,Fcaptured".
OL,10,FThe barrister showed the jury a
OL,11,Fstatement from another police officer,
OL,12,Fwhich stated Noah's school books were
OL,13,Fobserved in the flat "beside clothing
OL,14,Fon the bedroom floor".
OL,16,FMs Campbell said: "What we were
OL,17,Fparticularly interested in is what was
OL,18,Fthe clothing, and one way to answer
OL,19,Fthat question might have been through
OL,20,Fthe body-worn footage."
OL,26,@oD@SOUpD@IO]uD@VOUvD@UO]xD@SOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FThe barrister then said that during
OL,8,Fthe disclosure process in the inquest,
OL,9,Frequests had been made to view the
OL,10,Ffootage.
OL,12,FShe said this then led to a second
OL,13,Fstatement from the officer in 2022
OL,14,Fstating he could not remember if a
OL,15,Fbody-worn camera had been activated
OL,16,Fduring the search.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FThe barrister next drew attention to
OL,8,Fpolice public appeals for information
OL,9,Fduring the period of Noah's
OL,10,Fdisappearance, which had mentioned his
OL,11,Fmissing green coat.
OL,13,FShe said an anonymous call to police
OL,14,Ffollowing these appeals had led to the
OL,15,Fsearch of Paul's flat.
OL,17,FMs Campbell said: "The one thing you
OL,18,Fcame away without, which is of
OL,19,Finterest to us, was the green North
OL,20,FFace coat."
OL,26,@yD@SOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G17/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44518
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FHe said: "That is correct."
OL,9,FShe said: "That is because, I am going
OL,10,Fto suggest, you were never asked to
OL,11,Flook for it?"
OL,13,FThe officer said: "I can't recall the
OL,14,Ffull details of what we were told."
OL,16,FMr Justice Rooney asked the officer:
OL,17,F"Knowing you are going to arrest
OL,18,Fsomeone, would you not have put your
OL,19,Fbody-worn videos on?"
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@[O]qD@KOUsD@MO]uD@SOUvD@cO]yD@
OL,26,AAOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G18/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
