OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44519
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774552271
OL,3,CConstable unable to explain evidence
OL,4,Cthat he searched for Noah Donohoe's
OL,5,Ccoat
OL,7,FMr Wharry said: "I would only put it
OL,8,Fon if somebody is there."
OL,10,FCounsel for the PSNI Donal Lunny asked
OL,11,Fif there was an "element of
OL,12,Fdiscretion" for officers at the time
OL,13,Fabout when they turned their cameras
OL,14,Fon.
OL,16,FThe constable said: "There was, the
OL,17,Fsystem has changed since then."
OL,19,FThe inquest will resume on Monday.
OL,26,@oD@QOUpD@YO]sD@QOUtD@KO]xD@UOUyD@_O]
